<DOCOLDNO>IA007-000070-B001-288</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/euforic/cce/coljan9.htm 193.128.6.150 19970222015850 text/html 7016
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sat, 22 Feb 1997 01:58:36 GMT
