<BR>					
a:	Programme Countries
<BR>
b:	Transitional Development Assistance and Project Discontinuation										
<BR>
c:	Human Rights and Democratization					
<BR>
d:	Mixed Credits Scheme							
<BR>
<BR>
<B><FONT SIZE=3>4.	Regional Development Cooperation</FONT></B>					
<BR>
<BR>
<B><FONT SIZE=3>5.	Multilateral Development Cooperation</FONT></B>					
<BR>
a:	Multilateral Policy
<BR>								
b:	The UN System									
<BR>
c:	Development Banks								
<BR>
d:	Global Environmental Programmes					
<BR>
e:	Multi Bilateral Development Assistance				
<BR>
f:	Humanitarian Assistance						
