<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/euforic/cce/colnov28.htm 193.128.6.150 19970222020015 text/html 7152
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sat, 22 Feb 1997 02:00:01 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5
