<DOCNO>WT17-B17-69</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA082-000576-B038-86</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/euforic/planete/33lb.htm 193.128.6.150 19970213141844 text/html 12557
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Thu, 13 Feb 1997 14:18:23 GMT
