<DOCOLDNO>IA081-000563-B040-425</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/index_oc/9602/saudi.html 193.128.6.150 19970213111807 text/html 11157
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
