<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/iied/europe/bp11_gb.html 193.128.6.150 19970222014925 text/html 22047
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sat, 22 Feb 1997 01:49:03 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5
