http://www.ecdpm.org:80/euforic/cce/coljan29.htm 193.128.6.150 19970213135450 text/html 6930
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Thu, 13 Feb 1997 13:54:26 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Mon, 03 Feb 1997 23:00:58 GMT
