<h2>New Internationalist UN Reform Game</h2>
<hr>
<p>
<h3>A direct hit
by a mortar from the surrounding hills.</h3>
<p>

<p>
The more vetos there
are, the more likely the UN is to be stalled. Better to create a
new status of non-veto-holding permanent member.
<p>
