<head>
<title>NI UN reform - Dec 94</title>
<!!keys: New Internationalist+UN>
</head>
<body>
<h2>New Internationalist UN Reform Game</h2>
<hr>
<p>
<h3>Pass on.</h3>
<p>
It doesn't sound spectacular but
it's as good an outcome as we can hope for at the moment.
<p>


<p>
<b>Your next problem is the veto. On big issues all five permanent
members currently have a veto.<br>
How would you change this?</b>
<p>
<a href="NIreform7.html">1. Scrap the veto</a>
<p>
<a href="NIreform8.html">2. Extend the veto to new permanent members</a>
<p>
<a href="NIreform9.html">3. Rule that the veto only applies if two permanent members agree
to exercise it</a><p>

</body>
