<h2>New Internationalist UN Reform Game</h2>
<hr>
<p>
<h3>You fell
victim to friendly fire.</h3>
<p>

<p>
It sounds good but probably wouldn't
work. The biggest countries within the South's regions cannot
easily represent the interests of their neighbours. Can you
honestly see Pakistan feeling represented by India? Or Algeria
by Nigeria?
