<font face=ariel,helvetica><h6 align=left>The material that follows has been provided by
<a
href="../info/index.html">ACTIONAID</a></h6><br clear=right>
<br>
<h1 align=center> Donate Your Empty Toner Cartridge </h1>

<h3>Help People and the Environment</h3>

Since 1994, nearly 200,000 cartridges have been collected by 8,000 active donors and
given to ACTIONAID. The cartridges are sold to be remanufactured, which saves energy and
reduces waste. By donating empty toner cartridges to ACTIONAID, you can help raise funds
for our overseas woek - every cartricge enables us to help more of the world's poorest
people.<p>

<img align=left border=1 hspace=5 vspace=5 width=13 height=12 src="browny.gif">Donate your
empty toner cartridgs and we will  collect them <b>free</b> of charge using a national
carrier service.<p>


<img align=left border=1 hspace=5 vspace=5 width=13 height=12 src="browny.gif">Call our
collections number (0117 - 929 - 7992) to arrange your cartridge collection.
We prefer to collect in batches of 6 or more, if possible, though we will collect smaller
quantities if necessary. This helps us to keep our costs low, so even more money goes to
our overseas work.<p>


<img align=left border=1 hspace=5 vspace=5 width=13 height=12 src="browny.gif">If you have
just inkjet cartridges we prefer to collect 10 at a time or we can send you freepost
bags.<p>


<img align=left border=1 hspace=5 vspace=5 width=13 height=12 src="browny.gif">Please
place the cartridges into their boxes to protect them during transport.<p>


<img align=left border=1 hspace=5 vspace=5 width=13 height=12 src="browny.gif">You will
receive a certificate showing the amount your cartridges have raised for ACTIONAID.<p>


<img align=left border=1 hspace=5 vspace=5 width=13 height=12
src="browny.gif">Remanufactured Cartridges - If you are interested in purchasing
remanufactured cartridges we can put you in touch with a supplier. We would continue to
collect your empty cartridges in the usual way. <p>

<img align=left border=1 hspace=10 vspace=10 width=233 height=33 src="cartridges.jpg"><br
clear=all>
We have listed the cartridges that we collect by their type and reference no. rather than
by the printers they are used in. You should find this number on the cartridge box or on
the cartridge itself.

These cartridges are used in a large range of printers, faxes and copiers.<p>

